              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The target was composed of several foils of natural",
                "erbium, thickness 11.28-mg/cm**2, purity 99.9%.",
                "Aluminium and copper foils were interleaved in erbium",
                "stack to degrade the beam energy and to monitor the ion",
                "current and maximum incident energy."
              ]
